cu.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to 0 (invalid range, must be > 0) will cause cell identification failure and prevent proper network attachment.

du.explanation_en: Setting tr_s_preference to 'invalid' (unknown enum) will cause transport preference parsing failure and F1 interface setup error.
du.explanation_zh: 將 tr_s_preference 設定為 'invalid'（未知枚舉）會導致傳輸偏好解析失敗並造成 F1 介面設定錯誤。
